&quot;; //调用移动构造函数，掏空str，掏空后，最好不要使用str v.push_back(std::move(str)); std::cout &lt;&lt; &quot;After move, str is \&quot;&quot; &lt;&lt; str &lt;&lt; &quot;\&quot;
&quot;; std::cout &lt;&lt; &quot;The contents of the vector are \&quot;&quot; &lt;&lt; v[0] &lt;&lt; &quot;\&quot;, \&quot;&quot; &lt;&lt; v[1] &lt;&lt; &quot;\&quot;
&quot;; } Cout: After copy, str is &quot;Hello&quot; After move, str is &quot;&quot; The contents of the vector are &quot;Hello&quot;, &quot;Hello&quot; 函数原型 template &lt;typename T&gt; typename remove_reference&lt;T&gt;::type&amp;&amp; move(T&amp;&amp; t) { return static_cast&lt;typename remove_reference&lt;T&gt;::type&amp;&amp;&gt;(t); } 原型定义中的原理实现: 公式一）X&amp; &amp;、X&amp;&amp; &amp;、X&amp; &amp;&amp;都折叠成X&amp;，用于处理左值
